      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Integrating this capability with a convolutional neural network, we build an end-to-end model for predicting structure from spectra that is fast and accurate... During training, we passed the processed 1H NMR spectra through a one-dimensional convolutional neural network (CNN) to downsample the signal into a lower-dimensional space... These features were then passed through a full encoder-decoder transformer for structure elucidation",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes CNN-transformer pipeline architecture and demonstrates comparative analysis across modalities (1H only, 13C only, 1H+13C).",
