    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "During training, we passed the processed 1H NMR spectra through a one-dimensional convolutional neural network (CNN) to downsample the signal into a lower-dimensional space.",
      "asbval:note": "CNN role explicitly confirmed for 1H NMR feature extraction and downsampling.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1021_acscentsci_4c01132",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "tools",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "convolutional neural network (CNN) encoder - Extracts spectral feature vectors from 1D NMR spectra; compresses peak patterns into a dense latent representation",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T10:05:15.033734+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000338"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "These features were then passed through a full encoder-decoder transformer for structure elucidation, which outputs SMILES strings, and a transformer encoder for substructure elucidation, which outputs substructure probability arrays... The highest accuracy of 69.6% (Table 1, third row) is obtained when using both the 1H and 13C NMR spectra with a pretrained transformer for structure elucidation.",
      "asbval:note": "Transformer confirmed for structure and substructure prediction in multitask framework.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1021_acscentsci_4c01132",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "tools",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "transformer architecture - Assembles molecular fragments predicted by the CNN into a complete molecular structure; jointly predicts molecular formula and connectivity via multitask learning heads.",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T10:05:15.033734+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000338"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction/006",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "the transformer generates a SMILES string token by token... 15 predictions were generated for each input... the prediction was considered correct if one of these molecules, upon canonicalization, matched the exact canonical SMILES of the actual molecule.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper outputs SMILES strings with multiple ranked predictions (top-15).",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1021_acscentsci_4c01132",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "expected_outputs",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Molecular structure predictions (formula and connectivity) as SMILES strings ranked by confidence",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T10:05:15.033734+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000338"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction/007",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The multitask model also outputs a prediction for the target molecule's substructure profile, which can be interpreted as the probability of a given molecular fragment being present in the molecule based on its NMR spectra. These profiles, which provide additional information as to which of the 957 substructures are present in the system",
      "asbval:note": "Substructure probability outputs confirmed for 957 fragments.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1021_acscentsci_4c01132",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "expected_outputs",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Substructure probability profiles indicating presence/absence of 957 molecular fragments",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T10:05:15.033734+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000338"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Weights from a transformer pretrained on the substructure-to-structure task are used to initialize the multitask model... Without using the pretrained transformer, the structure elucidation accuracy drops significantly from 69.6% to 53.3%, demonstrating the importance of the pretraining step",
      "asbval:note": "Pretraining strategy explicitly confirmed and shown to improve accuracy by 16.3 percentage points.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1021_acscentsci_4c01132",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "spectral-to-structure-mapping-prediction",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "methods",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Multitask learning with pretraining on substructure-to-structure task before spectrum-to-structure fine-tuning",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T10:05:15.033734+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
